I have worked VERY hard and for a long time to make this door as good as 
possible, and I have received much response from people telling me how gr8 this
door is. This gives me much inspiration for further developing. Thank you all for
the support!

This is the first update of SysDL for over a year! I have had VERY little time 
for coding because of my year in the army, but finally; now I'm back in bizz!
With a lot of inspiration a and urge to keep develop both this and other doors.

I can't see that there is much missing in this door (some minor features only)
so if YOU miss anything please @{"contact me !" LINK "HOWTOCONTACT"}

