* Changed the ANSI commands a bit for compablility with DayDream BBS

* Added possibility to restrict files on both username and access-level

* Changed some minor output bugs

Not VERY much new things in this version as you can see, it is more just to tell
everybody that this project is not dead (and neither is MGS!) and that I am back 
from the army and KICKING like never before!

@ENDNODE
